---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Request Received | Sydney Anxiety Psychology"
  description="Your request has been received. A telehealth psychologist specialising in anxiety will contact you within 1 business day."
>
  <div class="main-content">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 560px; text-align: center; padding-top: 4rem;">

      <div style="background: var(--color-accent-light); border-radius: 50%; width: 64px; height: 64px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem; font-size: 1.75rem;">
        &#10003;
      </div>

      <h1 style="font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2rem); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Request received.</h1>

      <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">A telehealth psychologist specialising in anxiety will be in touch within <strong>1 business day</strong> to introduce themselves and discuss availability.</p>

      <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">You are under no obligation to proceed. The contact is purely to establish whether there is a suitable fit.</p>

      <div class="info-box" style="text-align: left; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <p><strong>In the meantime, it may be worth:</strong></p>
        <ul style="margin-top: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0;">
          <li>Booking an appointment with your GP to get a Mental Health Treatment Plan. This unlocks Medicare rebates and can reduce your out-of-pocket cost by $98.95 per session. <a href="/guides/cost-telehealth-psychologist-australia/">How MHTPs work &rarr;</a></li>
          <li>Reading about what to expect from your first session. <a href="/guides/how-telehealth-psychology-works/">Guide to how telehealth psychology works &rarr;</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary);">If you need urgent support, please contact <strong>Lifeline on 13 11 14</strong> or <strong>Beyond Blue on 1300 22 4636</strong>. This directory is not a crisis service.</p>

      <a href="/" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-accent);">&larr; Back to the directory</a>

    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
